 <span data-ttu-id="c0a7a-133"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>コンス トラクターをスロー、<xref:System.FormatException>次の状況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0a7a-133">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
