-   <span data-ttu-id="c0a7a-136">`id` "NULL"または"VOID"または「ガベージ」です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0a7a-136">`id` is "NULL" or "VOID" or "GARBAGE".</span></span>  
  
